name: MIS Flag Report
description:
The report produces a list of Active In, Active Out and Active UAL prisoners with an alert; the alerts are restricted to MAS,MEP,MFL,MHT,MSI,MSP,XEL,V46,VJOP, V45,VOP,OPPO,SR,RDO,RCC,RCS, SC,XCC, XCH,ROH,ROM and ROV.
PDD0019 - v00.00.07 Last Modified: 19/05/09

dataset.name: Flag Report Data
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT DISTINCT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.INITIALS, CASE WHEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE END, AT_CELL.UNIT_4_SHORT_DESCRIPTION, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MAIN_LEGAL_STATUS_CODE, AT_ALERT.ALERT_CODE_NK, AT_ALERT.ALERT_DESCRIPTION, AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_STATUS, rpad(AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME,35,'A'), AT_CELL.UNIT_4_DESCRIPTION FROM BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT, ( Select ALERT_SK, ALERT_CODE_NK from BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT where ALERT_CODE_NK IN('MAS','MEP','MFL','MHT',(SELECT establishment_code from prompt_),'MSP','XEL','V46','VJOP','V45','VOP','OPPO','SR','RDO','RCC','RCS','SC','XCC','XCH','ROH','ROM','ROV') ) DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_CELL, BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT AT_ALERT, BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_ALERT AT_OFFENDER_ALERT WHERE ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.BIRTH_DATE_SK=AT_DOB.DATE_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_ALERT.ALERT_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_SK ) AND ( AT_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK=AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK ) AND ( AT_CELL.UNIT_4_SK=AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_SK ) AND ( AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ACTIVE_FLAG='Y' ) AND ( DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS.ALERT_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID=CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER((SELECT username FROM context_ /*= #Variable('BOUSER') */ )) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= to_char(sysdate,'YYYY')-6 ) ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_STATUS IN ( 'Active In','Active Out' ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND='Y' ) AND ( AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for all)','A','Establishment\Establishment Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:69) */ ) Or 'All' in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for all)','A','Establishment\Establishment Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:69) */ ) ) AND ( case when 'All' in (SELECT WING FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Wing (All for all)','A','Cell\Unit Description 1',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:80) */ ) then 'All' else AT_CELL.UNIT_1_DESCRIPTION end in @Variable('Wing (All for all)') ) AND ( DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS.ALERT_CODE_NK in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Code (All for all)','A','Alerts\Restricted Alert Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:106) */ ) Or 'All' in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Code (All for all)','A','Alerts\Restricted Alert Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:106) */ ) ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_STATUS in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Status (All for all)','A','Alerts\Alert Status',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:107) */ ) Or 'All' in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Status (All for all)','A','Alerts\Alert Status',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:107) */ ) ) AND DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS.ALERT_CODE_NK IN ( 'MAS','MEP','MFL','MHT',(SELECT establishment_code from prompt_),'MSP','OPPO','RCC','RCS','RDO','ROH','ROM','ROV','SC','SR','V45','V46','VJOP','VOP','XCC','XCH','XEL' ) ) UNION SELECT DISTINCT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.INITIALS, CASE WHEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE END, '-', AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MAIN_LEGAL_STATUS_CODE, AT_ALERT.ALERT_CODE_NK, AT_ALERT.ALERT_DESCRIPTION, AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_STATUS, rpad(AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME,35,'A'), '-' FROM ( Select ALERT_SK, ALERT_CODE_NK from BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT where ALERT_CODE_NK IN('MAS','MEP','MFL','MHT',(SELECT establishment_code from prompt_),'MSP','XEL','V46','VJOP','V45','VOP','OPPO','SR','RDO','RCC','RCS','SC','XCC','XCH','ROH','ROM','ROV') ) DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB, BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT AT_ALERT, BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_ALERT AT_OFFENDER_ALERT, BODIMIS.FACT_MOVEMENT_EXTERNAL AT_FACT_MOV_EXT, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_EXT_MOV_FROM WHERE ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.BIRTH_DATE_SK=AT_DOB.DATE_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_ALERT.ALERT_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_SK ) AND ( AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK ) AND ( case when AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.FROM_LOCATION_TYPE = 'Establishment' then AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.FROM_LOCATION_SK end = AT_ESTABLISHMENT_EXT_MOV_FROM.ESTABLISHMENT_SK(+) ) AND ( DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS.ALERT_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID=CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER((SELECT username FROM context_ /*= #Variable('BOUSER') */ )) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= to_char(sysdate,'YYYY')-6 ) ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_STATUS = 'Active UAL' AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND='Y' ) AND ( AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y' ) AND ( AT_ESTABLISHMENT_EXT_MOV_FROM.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for all)','A','External Movements\Movement Location From Code (External)',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:61) */ ) Or 'All' in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for all)','A','External Movements\Movement Location From Code (External)',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:61) */ ) ) AND AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.REASON_CODE = 'UAL' AND AT_FACT_MOV_EXT.DIRECTION_CODE = 'OUT' AND ( DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS.ALERT_CODE_NK in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Code (All for all)','A','Alerts\Restricted Alert Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:106) */ ) Or 'All' establishment_code from prompt_),'MSP','OPPO','RCC','RCS','RDO','ROH','ROM','ROV','SC','SR','V45','V46','VJOP','VOP','XCC','XCH','XEL' ) ) UNION SELECT DISTINCT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.INITIALS, CASE WHEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE < '31/12/9000' THEN AT_DOB.DAY_DATE END, '-', AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MAIN_LEGAL_STATUS_CODE, AT_ALERT.ALERT_CODE_NK, AT_ALERT.ALERT_DESCRIPTION, AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_STATUS, rpad(AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME,35,'A'), '-' FROM BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP, ( Select ALERT_SK, ALERT_CODE_NK from BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT where ALERT_CODE_NK IN('MAS','MEP','MFL','MHT',(SELECT establishment_code from prompt_),'MSP','XEL','V46','VJOP','V45','VOP','OPPO','SR','RDO','RCC','RCS','SC','XCC','XCH','ROH','ROM','ROV') ) DT_RESTRICTED_ALERTS, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_DOB, BODIMIS.DIM_ALERT AT_ALERT, BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_ALERT AT_OFFENDER_ALERT WHERE ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.BIRTH_DATE_SK=AT_DOB.DATE_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_ALERT.ALERT_SK(+)=AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_SK ) AND ( BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID=CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER((SELECT username FROM context_ /*= #Variable('BOUSER') */ )) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= ( 'Active In','Active Out' ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND='Y' ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_ALERT.ALERT_STATUS in (SELECT UNKNOWN_PARAMETER FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Alert Status (All for Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:106) */ ) ) AND ( AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for all)','A','Associated Establishment\Associated Establishment Code',multi,free,Not_Persistent,User:69) */ ) Or 'All' in (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #Prompt('Establishment Code (All for (SELECT FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: MIS Load
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.BUSINESS_DATE FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE (BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.LOAD_ID = (SELECT MAX(LOAD_ID) FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE NOT LOAD_END_DATETIME IS NULL))), dataset_ AS (SELECT BUSINESS_DATE FROM dataset_base_)
